
DialogID_82050=<font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >You did well.</font>
DialogID_82051=<font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >Thank you so much. I have already prepared the clothing and Gold Sore Medicine.</font>
DialogID_82052=<font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >The medicine is finally here.</font>
DialogID_82053=<font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >I didn't expect you to be able to jump up here.</font>
DialogID_82054=<font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >Look, this is the half of the belly band</font><font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >.</font>
DialogID_82061=<font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >My child, give me back my child. </font><font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >Have you seen my child?</font>
SubmitNpcEx_57057=In order to rescue the Four Great Outlaws, go to <a href="findnpc_new,city03,EventNPCxszhh_4nei_fgxsh" style="HLStype1">Mirror Lake </a>in Jinling. Find <a href="findnpc_new,city03,NPCxszhh_4nei_yuming" style="HLStype1">Yu Weitian </a>and try to find out the details.
SubmitNpcEx_57066=Someone was assigned to bring back the Purple Jade Cave Flute to the Scholars. What are the intentions of the Blade Sharpening Hall? Does he only want to test us after all our trouble? Let's put aside these questions, and go back to report to the <a href="findnpc_new,school03,npc_4neidh_jzt" style="HLStype1">Elder Manager</a>.
