okmenu_82050=<font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >I have already notified all Elders, he won't be able to escape</font><font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >.</font>
okmenu_82051=<font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >Thank you.</font>
okmenu_82052=<font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >Hurry </font><font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >and change your clothing.</font>
okmenu_82053=<font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >It's very easy!</font>
okmenu_82054=<font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >Bring it to me.</font>
okmenu_82061=<font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >What nonsense is he talking about?</font>
story_82041_1=<font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >You must have heard about the Blade Sharpening Hall. This Blade Sharpening Hall is very arrogant and seems to dismiss the Eight Schools. Our Scholars' Disciples have been working hard, and have collected many clues.</font>
story_82041_2=<font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >All the sheepskin fragments we've collected appear as parts of a musical score. This is another riddle!</font>
story_82042_1=<font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >What sheepskin fragments? Let me take a look (Yun Yan picks up the sheepskin fragments and looks at them closely. She looks very fetching when she's concentrating.)</font>
story_82042_2=<font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >Ah, it's full of Tadpole characters. I don't understand them.</font>
story_82043_1=<font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >True knowledge comes when one knows the limitations of one's knowledge.</font>
story_82043_2=<font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >Let me look at it closely. What is this </font><font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >weird writing</font><font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >? I don't understand it.</font>
story_82044_1=<font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >Let me look at it.</font>
story_82044_2=<font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >Ah! What are these little dots? Let me connect them together. Oh! I get it. Look, look. What do you see when these are all connected?</font>
story_82045_1=<font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >What have you found?</font>
story_82045_2=<font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >Ye Qiannian? So it is she. This is an important discovery.</font>
story_82050_1=<font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >Please report back to the leader. We won't let him escape if he shows up.</font>
story_82051_1=<font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >Please report back to the Lord, telling him to not to worry. We won't let him escape if he shows up.</font>
story_82052_1=<font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >I have never heard of this School with this name in Jianghu. Maybe it's a new power, or it is a fake name to cover up its true identity. The most important thing now is to find out this person's identity. I left qingfu bug blood on him in secret when I was fighting him earlier. As for solving the riddle, let the other Disciples take care of it.</font>
story_82052_2=<font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >As shown by the </font><font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >qingfu insect, that person left in the direction of Suzhou. You go to Suzhou and check if there are any clues.</font>
story_82053_1=<font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >I'm very angry just talking about </font><font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >this</font><font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >. There was a </font><font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >gravely wounded </font><font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >mute </font><font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >who came through here, foolishly asking for direction. I couldn't understand his gestures so I scolded him a little bit. Who would have known that the mute would fly into a rage and attack me in broad daylight? He showed great Kung Fu skill even though he was already injured. I was wounded by him during our fight and as a result, got blood stains on me. It's fortunate that there were many people around. Due to his grave injury, the mute gave up and ran away.</font>
story_82053_2=<font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >What kind of person are you? I'm gravely injured by someone, and you didn't even show any concern, but only wanted to ask me questions. I know where the mute has gone. </font><font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >I haven't eaten for many days, and I have to spend so much time talking to you. You must buy me new clothing and give me Gold Sore Medicine, otherwise I won't tell you anything, even if you </font><font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >beat me to death.</font>
story_82054_1=<font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >I have some clothing with me, but you have to do something for me.</font>
story_82054_2=<font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >There are some rotten Taoists who have been oppressing the village people. I ask Young Hero to teach them a harsh lesson.</font>
story_82055_1=<font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >We brought some with us when going out to cut wood. I will give you Gold Sore Medicine as well if you can help me with this.</font>
story_82055_2=<font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >Those Swordsmen and rotten Taoists work hand in hand. I ask Young Hero to teach them a lesson.</font>
story_82056_1=
story_82057_1=<font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >Heh-heh. </font><font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >Thank you, Young Hero. But I'm not 100% sure where he ran to.</font>
story_82057_2=<font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >Don't worry, Young Hero. Although I didn't see it clearly, others did. I have a </font><font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >Constable </font><font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >friend who followed after that mute in secret, and he saw the mute went to Gold Silkworm Village.</font>
story_82058_1=<font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >Ah, it's a long story. As a Constable in the Ming Court, I couldn't even catch a mute. You should immediately go to the Forest over there, and don't let him escape.</font>
story_82059_1=<font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >The mute servant had already left here. Although your Headmaster wounded him, you came too late. He had mostly recovered from his injury. You won't be able to fight him even if you catch up to him. And he didn't have your School's lost treasure with him.</font>
story_82059_2=<font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >All the Eight Schools' thing was taken by the Young Hall Leader. I would advise you to go back to your own School and start to deal with the matter according to the mute servant's instructions.</font>
story_82059_3=<font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >I told you that this much is enough</font><font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >. </font><font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >I have had enough. Get lost! Your School's thing might not be there if you go back too late.</font>
story_82060_1=<font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >You are finally home. It looks like you are wounded. What happened?</font>
story_82060_2=<font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >I see. What else have you found out?</font>
story_82060_3=<font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >We need to discuss this matter further. It seems like they have found out about our pursuit of the mute. He had someone present an ultimatum before your arrival, saying that he would </font><font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >destroy all the stolen treasures if we didn't follow his instructions.</font>
story_82060_4=
story_82071_1=<font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >It looks like we can only investigate Ye Qiannian in secret.</font>
story_82071_2=<font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >The two Villa Leaders from the Zhuge House and Chuyun Villa engaged in a battle many years ago, which caused destruction to both sides. And then the Zhuge House and Chuyun Villa were wiped out mysteriously during the same night. After that, Ye Qiannian started talking nonsense, and her child went missing.</font>
story_82071_3=<font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >Now we can only try to find the survivors and ask them information about Ye Qiannian. </font><font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >I heard that a survivor of the massacre now lives in the Double Dragons Market. You go and investigate it.</font>
story_82072_1=<font face="Default" color="#ffffff" ></font><font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >Why </font><font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >would people ask about this after so many years have passed?</font>
story_82072_2=<font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >Because you Scholars have done some good things in our Village, I </font><font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >will </font><font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >help you. This survivor is named Zhu Agui, who is a well-known rogue in our Village. Young girls here steer away from him when they see him.</font>
story_82073_1=<font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >This...I don't know about this. I'm only a Housekeeper.</font>
story_82073_2=<font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >Great Hero, have mercy. I really don't know anything. Great Hero, you might not know that the Chuyun Villa and Zhuge House were longtime friends. Ye Qiannian of the Zhuge House often took her maid with her to visit the Chuyun Villa. I became the maid's lover after a while. The maid and I happened to out for a tryst on the day of the massacre. We found everybody was dead when we returned.</font>
story_82073_3=<font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >It has nothing to do with me. I'm only a Housekeeper. Let me think about it. Yes, one time Ye Qiannian's maid told me that the Chuyun Villa Leader was having a love affair with Ye Qiannian. </font><font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >I only found a half of a belly band on the scene after I returned to the Villa that day. I know nothing other than that.</font>
story_82074_1=<font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >Uh-huh? How do you know so much? Who are you?</font>
story_82074_2=<font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >belly band. This is the belly band. Hmm-hmm-hmm. After saying goodbye to Zhu Agui, I returned to the Zhuge House. I was stunned when I opened the door. Everyone in the Villa was dead, and Ye Qiannian was on the floor.</font>
story_82074_3=<font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >Ye Qiannian had just given birth but I couldn't find the baby anywhere. I was very scared, and I went to find Zhu Agui. We then took the valuables from the Villa and ran away.</font>
story_82075_1=<font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >This.... Isn't this </font><font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >my </font><font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >half belly band? (Ye Qiannian gets very emotional)</font>
story_82075_2=<font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >You, do you know were my child is?</font>
story_82075_3=<font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >That is the child I bore! Oh-oh. My poor child. </font><font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >I really miss you.</font>
story_82075_4=<font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >If you can help me find my child, I'll tell you where the Schools' treasures are.</font>
story_82101_1=<font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >According to intelligence, a Villa woman named Nangong Lingyan adopted a child. It's possible that child might be Ye Qiannian's child.</font>
story_82102_1=<font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >Qian Niang? She told me that she wanted to take me to look at the lotuses at the Residence of the Great Weiqi Master.</font>
story_82102_2=<font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >She has already gone there. Qian Niang acted very strangely. I was a little scared, so I didn't go with her.</font>
story_82103_1=<font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >Do you think I'm stupid? I won't give you the Purple Jade Cave Flute until I see her with my own eyes, and confirm it's her.</font>
story_82103_2=<font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >I'll bring the Purple Jade Cave Flute with me and wait for you at Guihu. You only need to bring my child over there.</font>
story_82104_1=<font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >Who are you? How do you know my name?</font>
story_82104_2=<font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >The birth mother? Why did she abandon me for so many years? Why would she want to see me when I've almost forgotten about her? Where is she?!</font>
story_82111_1=<font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >Serve the Imperial Court? They were only working together temporarily to defeat their mutual enemies. The Imperial Court used the opportunity and gave out the Imperial Edict Iron Tickets to the Eight Schools in order to bribe them.</font>
story_82111_2=<font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >More than 10 years ago, Zhu Yunwen fought against the current Emperor for the throne. At the time, Demonic forces prevailed over the Right Way in Wulin, and the Cultist had great power. The Cultist Leader publicly supported Zhu Yunwen. The Imperial Court and Wulin would have faced a big catastrophe if the Cultists and Zhu Yunwen had succeeded.</font>
story_82111_3=<font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >That's right. All the Schools teamed up with the Imperial Court and crushed the plot of the cultists and Zhu Yunwen. The cultists collapsed as a result, and Wulin escaped from a catastrophe. In order to reward the Eight Schools for putting down the rebellion, the Imperial Court specially issued the Imperial Edict Iron Tickets, which can be passed down through generations and can be used by the Schools to escape disasters at critical times.</font>
story_82112_1=<font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >The Lord is paying attention to the big picture. The Scholars won't be able to resist the Imperial Court if it really wants to find fault with us.</font>
story_82112_2=<font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >You have to think about it carefully. I would expel you from the Scholars and claim it has nothing to do with the Scholars, and say it's your personal action if the Imperial Court pursues the matter.</font>
story_82113_1=<font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >You should not meddle in this matter. You will only bring disaster to yourself if you act heedlessly. Maybe it was a mistake to raid the Execution Ground. Umm....</font>
story_82201_1=<font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >Ge Bufan gave me a baby girl to raise. The strange thing was that he also gave me a half belly band at the same time, saying it was the key to finding the girl's birth mother.</font>
story_82201_2=<font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >Shen Xiaolan, you might be able to find her at Libie Tomb if you want to see her. By the way, I once saw Ye Qiannian talking to the Little Saintly Girl. You should ask Gu Xinluo if you want to find Ye Qiannian.</font>
story_menu_82041=<font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >Lord, I heard you are in a hurry to find me. What happened?</font>
story_menu_82042=<font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >Sister Yun Yan, come and take a look for me. What is drawn on the Sheepskin Scroll Fragment?</font>
story_menu_82043=<font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >Ah-Song, </font><font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >I heard </font><font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >that you passed the Xiucai examination. I have a question here. Please check what is drawn on the Sheepskin Fragment for me.</font>
story_menu_82044=<font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >Master Shi, come and see what is drawn on this Sheepskin Fragment.</font>
story_menu_82045=<font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >Lord, I know what is drawn on the Sheepskin Fragment.</font>
story_menu_82050=<font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >The Lord gave the order to reinforce the defense and prevent an enemy ambush.</font>
story_menu_82051=<font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >The Lord gave the order to reinforce the defense and prevent an enemy ambush.</font>
story_menu_82052=<font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >How is the Blade Sharpening Hall sacred; have you heard, Lord?</font>
story_menu_82053=<font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >Where did you get these blood stains?</font>
story_menu_82054=<font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >Hello. Do you have clean clothing here?</font>
story_menu_82055=<font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >I was lucky that I didn't let you down. </font><font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >I would like to know where I can buy Gold Sore Medicine.</font>
story_menu_82056=<font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >I have finished the task.</font>
story_menu_82057=<font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >You got your clean clothing and Gold Sore Medicine, </font><font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >you can now tell me where the mute ran to.</font>
story_menu_82058=<font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >Constable Gong, what happened to you? </font><font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >Did that mute wound you?</font>
story_menu_82059=<font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >Now it's time for you to tell me the whereabouts of the mute.</font>
story_menu_82060=<font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >Lord, I'm here to pay my respects.</font>
story_menu_82071=<font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >Lord, Ye Qiannian is talking nonsense and it looks like she is insane. What should we do now?</font>
story_menu_82072=<font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >Village Leader, do you recall the massacres at the Zhuge House and Chuyun Villa that caused such a commotion at the time?</font>
story_menu_82073=<font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >You thug, aren't you going to tell me the truth now? How did you escape from the massacre at the </font><font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >Chuyun Villa </font><font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >at that time?</font>
story_menu_82074=<font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >You were Zhu Agui's lover at that time? How you know what happened at the Zhuge House massacre?</font>
story_menu_82075=<font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >Ye Qiannian, do you recognize this half a belly band?</font>
story_menu_82101=<font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >Have you found the location of Ye Qiannian's child?</font>
story_menu_82102=<font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >Little Saintly Girl, do you know where Ye Qiannian is?</font>
story_menu_82103=<font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >We already told you who your child is. I'll tell you her name once you hand over the Purple Jade Cave Flute.</font>
story_menu_82104=<font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >You are Shen Xiaolan, right?</font>
story_menu_82111=<font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >Why would the Imperial Court give the Imperial Edict Iron Tickets to the Eight Schools? Was it because the Eight Schools once joined forces with and served the Imperial Court?</font>
story_menu_82112=<font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >The Four Great Outlaws sent a petition written in blood, begging for help by carrier pigeon. The Lord has some misgivings, but I think....</font>
story_menu_82113=<font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >Lord, the Four Great Outlaws were the ones who escorted Ding Jiuzhong's wife Feng Fei and their son. But they were all killed by the Blade Sharpening Hall.</font>
story_menu_82201=<font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >I heard that you adopted a baby girl?</font>
storyinfo_82041=Lord <a href="findnpc_new,school03,WorldNpc03305" style="HLStype1">Xiao Bieqing </a>has something to say to you. Go and find him immediately.
storyinfo_82042=I can't make out what is drawn on this Sheepskin Scroll Fragment after working on it for a long time. Let's take it outside and let <a href="findnpc_new,school03,JZTNPC148" style="HLStype1">Yun Yan </a>take a look.
storyinfo_82043=I heard that <a href="findnpc_new,school03,jzt086" style="HLStype1">Shi Yangsong </a>passed the Xiucai examination. He must be very knowledgeable. Should we ask him?
storyinfo_82044=Everybody claims that <a href="findnpc_new,school03,WorldNpc03306" style="HLStype1">Shi Yanbing </a>of the Scholars is very intelligent. I'll ask him; maybe he will know something.
storyinfo_82045=I found after my fall that you have to look this Sheepskin Fragment up-side-down. Hurry and tell <a href="findnpc_new,school03,WorldNpc03305" style="HLStype1">Xiao Bieqing about this.</a>
