storyinfo_82055=Listen to <a href="findnpc_new,city02,sz468" style="HLStype1">Chun Ge</a>'s explanation.
storyinfo_82057=Listen to <a href="findnpc_new,city02,QYNpcmsjmy001" style="HLStype1">Long Shijian</a>'s explanation.
