storyinfo_82059=Listen to the <a href="findnpc_new,city02,NPC_4nei_gbj012" style="HLStype1">Mysterious Person</a>'s explanation.
storyinfo_82060=Go back to the Scholars and report to <a href="findnpc_new,school03,WorldNpc03305" style="HLStype1">Xiao Bieqing.</a>
storyinfo_82071=Ye Qiannian was talking nonsense and I couldn't get anything out of her. Let's go see <a href="findnpc_new,school03,WorldNpc03305" style="HLStype1">Xiao Bieqing </a>and discuss what to do next.
storyinfo_82072=Ask Village Leader <a href="findnpc_new,school03,WorldNpc03613" style="HLStype1">Zhao Zixing </a>about survivors of the massacre.
storyinfo_82073=Threaten <a href="findnpc_new,school03,WorldNpc03610" style="HLStype1">Zhu Agui </a>a little bit, make him tell you the truth about the massacre.
storyinfo_82074=Find the <a href="findnpc_new,school03,WorldNpc03686" style="HLStype1">maid </a>who was Zhu Agui's lover and ask her the truth about the massacre. (This girl often comes around here, so look carefully.)
storyinfo_82075=Take the half a belly band and confront <a href="findnpc_new,school03,npc_4nei_jzt_l01" style="HLStype1">Ye Qiannian</a>.
storyinfo_82101=The letter says that the clues about Ye Qiannian's child have been collected. Go back to the Scholars immediately, and talk to the <a href="findnpc_new,school03,npc_4neidh_jzt" style="HLStype1">Elder Manager </a>to learn the details.
storyinfo_82102=Nangong Lingyan said that Shen Xiaolan is Ye Qiannian's child. We are getting a lot of messages. It is said that Nangong Lingyan claimed that she once saw Lady Ye Qia and the Little Saintly Girl <a href="findnpc_new,school03,WorldNpc03320" style="HLStype1">Gu Xinluo </a>talking with each other. Go to the Little Saintly Girl and ask her where Lady Ye Qia is. It'll save you some time if you go by the <a href="findnpc,school03,801.147,114.934,61.203" style="HLStype1">mountain path</a>.
storyinfo_82103=The Little Saintly Girl Gu Xinluo said that <a href="findnpc_new,school03,npc_4nei_jzt_l01" style="HLStype1">Ye Qiannian </a>is looking at lotuses at the Residence of the Great Weiqi Master. Since we already know that Shen Xiaolan is Ye Qiannian's child, tell Ye Qiannian to prepare the Purple Jade Cave Flute to exchange for information.
storyinfo_82104=Ye Qiannian wants to see her daughter before she can hand over the Purple Jade Cave Flute. Now we need to take <a href="findnpc_new,school03,npc_4nei_jzt_l02" style="HLStype1">Shen Xiaolan </a>to Guihu and make Ye Qiannian hand over the Purple Jade Cave Flute as she promised.
storyinfo_82111=Go to the Scholars and listen to <a href="findnpc_new,school03,WorldNpc03305" style="HLStype1">Xiao Bieqing</a>'s explanation.
storyinfo_82112=Go to the Scholars and listen to the <a href="findnpc_new,school03,npc_4neidh_jzt" style="HLStype1">Elder Manager</a>'s explanation.
storyinfo_82113=Go back to the Scholars and report to <a href="findnpc_new,school03,WorldNpc03305" style="HLStype1">Xiao Bieqing.</a>
storyinfo_82201=The Elder Manager told you that Ye Qiannian's child was adopted by <a href="findnpc_new,school03,JZTNPC112" style="HLStype1">Nangong Lingyan</a>. Go and ask her. Perhaps you might be able to find out who Ye Qiannian's child is.
storymenu_82041_1=<font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >Lord, may I ask about the clues?</font>
storymenu_82041_2=<font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >Lord, Please don't worry. I'll do my very best.</font>
storymenu_82042_1=<font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >This important thing was given to me by the Lord, but I don't understand what it is about even after looking at it for a long time.</font>
storymenu_82042_2=<font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >Sister Yun Yan, it's okay, I'll go and ask other people.</font>
storymenu_82043_1=<font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >Ah, speak plainly. Take a look what it is drawn here.</font>
storymenu_82043_2=<font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >Give me a break. You passed the Xiucai examination, but you are still so unreliable. I had better ask someone else.</font>
storymenu_82044_1=<font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >Look at it carefully. This important thing was given to me by the Lord, who said it has great importance for us Scholars.</font>
storymenu_82044_2=<font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >What? Let me see, it says "Good Lady Young Person Ten Mouths" when these little dots are connected. </font><font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >What does that mean?</font>
storymenu_82045_1=<font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >I see. Look, it says "Good Lady Young Person Ten Mouths" when these little dots are connected. It says "Ye Qiannian" when you turn the paper up-side-down.</font>
storymenu_82045_2=<font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >Thank you, Lord. I discovered it by accident. Lord, what's the connection between Ye Qiannian </font><font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >and </font><font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >our </font><font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >Scholars</font><font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >?</font>
storymenu_82050_1=<font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >Elder, you'd better be careful. Our enemies are not weak.</font>
storymenu_82051_1=<font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >You better be careful, the enemies are not weak.</font>
storymenu_82052_1=<font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >I'll get the bottom of it.</font>
storymenu_82052_2=<font face="Default" color="#ffffff">I obey the order.</font>
storymenu_82053_1=Where did the mute go?
storymenu_82053_2=<font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >Wait here, I'll find you some clothing and Gold Sore Medicine.</font>
storymenu_82054_1=<font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >What's the matter? Speak up.</font>
storymenu_82054_2=<font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >This must be done.</font>
storymenu_82055_1=<font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >What's the matter this time?</font>
storymenu_82055_2=<font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >This must be done.</font>
storymenu_82057_1=<font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >You better not play with me.</font>
storymenu_82057_2=<font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >Gold Silkworm Village? I'll go and check it now.</font>
storymenu_82058_1=<font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >I'll go now.</font>
storymenu_82059_1=<font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >That? </font><font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >Do you have it?</font>
storymenu_82059_2=<font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >How do you know so much? Who are you?</font>
storymenu_82059_3=<font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >You! </font><font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >(This person possesses great Kung Fu skill. I'd better go back to the School and report it.)</font>
storymenu_82060_1=<font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >I'm incompetent. I was stopped by a Mysterious Person when chasing after the mute. I was defeated and lost the clue.</font>
storymenu_82060_2=<font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >But that Mysterious Person told me something. It seems the Eight Schools' stolen treasures were handed over to the Young Hall Leader of the Blade Sharpening Hall. It sounds like this Young Hall Leader has powerful backing, and I don't know how to find him.</font>
storymenu_82060_3=<font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >This Thief dares to threaten us!</font>
storymenu_82060_4=
storymenu_82071_1=<font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >Lord, what happened to Ye Qiannian at that time?</font>
storymenu_82071_2=<font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >I see. What should we do now?</font>
storymenu_82071_3=<font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >Yes, Lord. I'll go immediately.</font>
storymenu_82072_1=<font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >Ah, it's a long story. I heard that there is a massacre survivor living in the Village. I wonder if I can see him, as I have something important to seek from him.</font>
storymenu_82072_2=<font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >Where is this wretch? I'll go and teach him a lesson.</font>
storymenu_82073_1=<font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >Heh-heh. You are still not telling the truth. Do you want another beating from me?</font>
storymenu_82073_2=<font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >Heh-heh. You are lucky to live this long. I'm a </font><font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >descendant </font><font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >of the Chuyun Villa. I'm here to take your life. </font><font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >Hurry and tell me what else you know. Otherwise, I'll take your head as an offering for my ancestors.</font>
storymenu_82073_3=<font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >You are lucky this time. I'll allow you to live. </font><font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >Tell me, where can I find the maid? </font><font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >(I think I should go and ask that maid, maybe she will know something.)</font>
storymenu_82074_1=<font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >Heh-heh. Zhu Agui already gave me instructions. He returned this belly band to me.</font>
storymenu_82074_2=<font face="Default" color="#ffffff">The next?</font>
storymenu_82074_3=<font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >It seems that there is a close connection between this family ruin and Lady Ye Qian. He child went missing. Is Zhuge Yun the child of Lady Ye Qian? It looks like you'll have to go back to find Lady Ye Qian to get the whole story.</font>
storymenu_82075_1=<font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >Finally you are ready to talk.</font>
storymenu_82075_2=<font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >Isn't Zhuge Yun of Guili Mountain Villa your child?</font>
storymenu_82075_3=<font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >So, there are some untold stories behind this. What do you want with our Scholars? What's the connection between you and the Blade Sharpening Hall? Where is the Scholars' treasure? Speak up.</font>
storymenu_82075_4=<font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >Okay, I think I should go back and report to the Lord.</font>
storymenu_82101_1=<font face="Default" color="#ffffff">Okay. I will go to ask about it right away.</font>
storymenu_82102_1=<font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >Oh, when are you leaving?</font>
storymenu_82102_2=<font face="Default" color="#8fd6ef" >(Looks like she was scared by Ye Qiannian) </font><font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >Thanks a lot. I'll bring some Candied Haws to you next time.</font>
storymenu_82103_1=<font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >Alright, what are you going to do?</font>
storymenu_82103_2=<font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >Deal.</font>
storymenu_82104_1=<font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >Don't be afraid. Nangong Lingyan sent me to see you. We already know who your birth mother is.</font>
storymenu_82104_2=<font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >She is in Guihu. Maybe she had her difficulties. Go and ask her.</font>
storymenu_82111_1=<font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >What mutual enemies?</font>
storymenu_82111_2=<font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >So the Eight Schools joined forces with the Imperial Court and defeated the Cultists and Zhu Yunwen?</font>
storymenu_82111_3=<font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >That will be for everyone's benefit.</font>
storymenu_82112_1=<font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >What the Elder Manager says is absolutely right. But a Hero would not see a person dying and not save him. Not to mention that other Schools might think that the Scholars had submitted to the Imperial Court. So, I decided to rescue them myself.</font>
storymenu_82112_2=<font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >I have made up my mind. This can't be delayed. I'll go and rescue them right away.</font>
storymenu_82113_1=<font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >Why would the Sword Sharpening Hall refer to Ding Jiuzhong and the Four Great Outlaws as Cultists? We teamed up with the Imperial Court to defeat the Cultists back then. Why are we helping the Cultists now?</font>
storymenu_82201_1=<font face="Default" color="#8fd6ef" >(Half a belly band! Looks like the intelligence is correct. Nangong Lingyan indeed adopted Ye Qiannian's child. But what's the connection between Zhu Bufan and this baby girl? Could he know who the baby girl's birth mother is?) </font><font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >Oh? What's the girl's name? Maybe she's Ye Qiannian's child.</font>
storymenu_82201_2=<font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >Alright. Thanks a lot.</font>
DialogID_82002=<font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >This is the antidote. Pour it in the Scholar's </font><font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >water supply.</font>
QiecuoMenu_82001=<font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >Oh no, it's become crazed</font><font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >! (This disease is driving people mad)</font>
QiecuoTitle_82001=<font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >I'll kill you</font><font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >! </font>
