interactinfo_82002=Get antidote from<a href="findnpc_new,school03,Npc_5neijz_57036n_01" style="HLStype1">Mu Shuzi</a>.
okmenu_82002=<font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >Young lady, take good care of yourself!</font>
story_82013_1=<font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >Stop pretending! You were sent by Elder Huadi to kill me. You may look like a scholar, but </font><font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >the</font><font face="Default" color="#ffffff" > smell of the </font><font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >Five-Poison</font><font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >  is on you. Aside from Elder Huadi only two other people knew how to make this poison and they're long dead.  </font>
story_82013_2=<font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >I'll trust you for now. I believe Elder Huadi is responsible for the poison incident. I had ruined his plan when we were fighting for He's Jade in Luoyang. Now he is </font><font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >luring me</font><font face="Default" color="#ffffff" > out using the Scholars. </font>
story_82013_3=<font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >It goes back 20 years. My master was a member of the cult though his two disciples, myself and Yi Heng, who were not part of the cult. Elder Brother Yi Heng, could not be trusted so master decided </font><font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >to</font><font face="Default" color="#ffffff" > teach the school's ultimate skill </font><font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >to me only.</font>
story_82013_4=<font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >In retaliation, Yi Heng attempted to kill our master but ultimately failed. He then fled to Chongwang Valley to seek refuge with Elder Huadi</font><font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >. Months later, master passed away due to the wounds he received from Yi heng.</font><font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >I sought out Yi Heng with assistance from Xiao Bieqing and became engaged in battle with him and Elder Huadi. I was able to kill Yi Heng  and avenge my master but Bieqing was poisoned during the fight. As such I took him back to school to treat him. </font>
story_82013_5=<font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >When Xiao Bieqing discovered who my master was, he parted ways with me</font><font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >, though I knew he has secretly protecting me. </font><font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >Later, Elder Huadi came to seek vengeance and almost succeeded. Luckily, Xiao Bieqing had saved me; however, I was infected with Love Poison and now I cannot allow myself to fall in love or I would die. Since then, I have held a burning hatred for Elder Huadi. Xiao Bieqing felt that he could protect if i resided within the Scholars so I complied. </font>
story_82013_6=<font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >Now that Elder Huadi is here, I must confront him. Follow me, we'll find Xiao Bieqing and come up with a plan. </font>
story_82014_1=<font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >Mu Shuzi already informed me of the matter</font><font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >. She will lure out whomever was spreading the poison and we will apprehend them. </font>
story_82014_2=<font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >She insisted and I respect her choice. For now you need to eliminate the poison in the water before anyone else is infected. </font>
story_82020_1=<font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >Lately, disciples have been falling under a state of madness and others have been ill all day long. Physicians cannot figure out this disease and due to the risk of potential plague, the Scholars is currently quarantined.</font>
story_82021_1=<font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >(Crying)</font>
story_82022_1=<font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >Let me see...Hmmm, I have never seen anything like it. Sorry, I can't help you with this.</font><font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >Although</font><font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >, is this vomit is coming from those who are poisoned, you might want to speak with Shi Yanbing. He is knowledgeable regarding these matters. </font>
story_82023_1=<font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >Hmm? What did the Great Physician say? </font>
story_82023_2=<font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >Poisoned? Show me the vomit...I see. It is no ordinary poison. What's this? There are some lotus pieces in there. Could it this person have been poisoned from drinking water near Ink Pond? I need you to collect some water samples from the fall near the Ink Pond for me. </font>
story_menu_82013=<font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >Lady, why are you fighting</font><font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >? </font>
story_menu_82014=<font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >Leader, there is something I would like to report.</font><font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >It's </font><font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >regarding the strange disease in the school</font><font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >.</font>
story_menu_82020=<font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >Uncle, </font><font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >why are we closing off the hill? </font>
story_menu_82021=<font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >Are you alright? </font>
story_menu_82022=<font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >Sir, I have some vomit collected from sick disciples. Would you mind examining it? </font>
story_menu_82023=<font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >Uncle Shi, </font><font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >I have collected the vomit from sick disciples for the Great Physician to inspect</font><font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >. </font>
