storyinfo_82023=Show the vomit to <a href="findnpc_new,school03,WorldNpc03306" style="HLStype1">Shi Yanbing</a>.
storymenu_82013_1=<font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >You are mistaken. I am a disciple of the Scholars and I was investigating the case before I was assaulted. The </font><font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >smell on me was the poison powder from the attacker</font><font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >. If I was sent by Elder Huadi, we wouldn't be having this talk.</font>
storymenu_82013_2=<font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >Elder Huadi wanted to capture you.</font><font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >Why is he targeting the Scholars</font><font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >? We were not at odds with each other.</font>
storymenu_82013_3=<font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >Doctor? Evil Cult? </font>
storymenu_82013_4=<font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >Is the leader alright? </font>
storymenu_82013_5=<font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >I have never heard such a story about the school leader before! </font>
storymenu_82013_6=<font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >Thank you.</font>
storymenu_82014_1=<font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >Good idea</font><font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >, though we do not know what kind of enemies we are facing. Not to mention Mu will be in danger. </font>
storymenu_82014_2=<font face="Default" color="#ffffff">I obey the order.</font>
storymenu_82020_1=<font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >So that's why! </font>
storymenu_82021_1=<font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >He's gone completely mad. He won't be of any help.</font>
storymenu_82022_1=<font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >Poisoned? </font><font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >Thank you anyway. </font>
storymenu_82023_1=<font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >The Great Physician himself has never seen such a disease before and he believed it was caused by poison. </font>
storymenu_82023_2=<font face="Default" color="#ffffff">I obey the order.</font>
